    {"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Cultural Context"}],"depth":2,"type":"heading"},
    {"children":[{"type":"text","value":"深入 reflects Chinese intellectual values that emphasize thorough understanding over superficial\nknowledge. In Chinese academic and professional culture, 深入 investigation is highly respected,\nrepresenting the scholarly ideal of comprehensive mastery. The concept embodies the belief that true\nwisdom comes from deep, rather than shallow, exploration."}],"type":"paragraph"}
